# Domain redirects: drq.xyz → drqsatoshin.com
https://drq.xyz/* https://drqsatoshin.com/:splat 301!
https://www.drq.xyz/* https://drqsatoshin.com/:splat 301!

# Domain redirects: drq.com → drqsatoshin.com
https://drq.com/* https://drqsatoshin.com/:splat 301!
https://www.drq.com/* https://drqsatoshin.com/:splat 301!

# Mirror.xyz integration
/mirror https://mirror.xyz/drqsatoshin.eth 301!
/mirror/* https://mirror.xyz/drqsatoshin.eth/:splat 301!
/blog https://mirror.xyz/drqsatoshin.eth 301!

# SPA fallback (must be last)
